Everything attached to me wins! ✨

Cheers to 7 years in business! 04.16.2016. The business that I started at just 16 years old.

I didn’t really know WHAT I was doing when I started, I just put myself out there and learned along the way. I got 12 shirts made, had a photoshoot in the park, made my own website, and it took off from there! Through high school, active duty military, and college I still held onto my dream of being an entrepreneur & just enjoyed the journey. I thank God that He allowed me to grow into this entrepreneur & didn’t give me everything all at once!

My brand really represents who I am. I’m always speaking life and positivity into others. It was always about the impact I would make when I started; the income was just a bonus.

Over the years, I stopped thinking like a small business owner & started thinking like one that wanted to touch 6 & 7 figures. No one sees the work you put in behind closed doors, they only see the success. But I’m proud to say that I never gave up. I speak life and prosperity over my business everyday, and I wouldn’t be who I am today if I never started this. Wow, thank You God! From nowhere to NOW HERE!

I hope this encourages someone to just START the business or to KEEP GOING! I’m rooting for you! 🙌🏾 God is capable of doing great things in and through you! Get out of your own way, trust Him & take off!

Link to my site in bio 🔥

So 6 days in Turks & Caicos was wayy too many reels to make one by one so here’s a recap of all six days in 30 seconds 🤣 

I had soo much fun there! I felt a sense of peace that I hadn’t felt in a while & I love that for me 🤍 I definitely gotta go back! The whole experience was AMAZING! Details below ⬇️ 

Where we stayed: Villa Del Mar & Ports of Call Resort

Excursions: Horseback riding: TCI Heritage
Parasailing: Key to the Sea Parasailing
Full Day Cruise: Caicos Dream Tours @caicosdreamtours 
Massages: Spa Nadia Salon
Birthday Celebration: Shisha Lounge @theshishaloungetci 

Restaurants: The Terrace, Danny Buoys, Coco Bistro, Mr. Grouper’s, Fish Fry (go on Thursdays), Da Conch Shack (go on Wednesdays), Island Scoop, Bugaloos

Beach: Grace Bay 🌊

Travel Agent: me 🤣 lol BOOK THAT TRIP!

Transparent moment: Today makes two months since I lost my favorite person, my papa.🤍 The only thing that’s been getting me thru is my strong relationship w/ God & my amazing support system 🙏🏾

Losing him really put into perspective that I needed to take a step back and focus on what really matters in life.

I could’ve lost my mind ( and at times it felt like I was ) but I held onto God’s Word and used my grief to grow closer to Him.
 
I just kept telling myself, if I was following God before this, I’m DEFINITELY about to stick close to Him now! I feel God’s peace over my life more than ever now & I’m so grateful 🫶🏾 I know that I am exactly where God wants me to be. 

No matter what the enemy throws my way, GOD IS ON MY SIDE and His plan for me will always prevail 🤍 #watchtiltheend #peace #love #joy #daybyday #Godiswithme #GIWM #healing
